title: BREAKING: Woman with 'CAR BOMB' forces police to shut down busy bridge in California
text:
BREAKING: Woman with 'CAR BOMB' forces police to shut down busy bridge in California BREAKING: Woman with 'CAR BOMB' forces police to shut down busy bridge in California A BOMB threat has forced police to shut down a busy bridge after a woman claimed to have turned her car into a bomb, according to reports. PUBLISHED: 00:31,  37, Wed, Feb 1, 2017 Ioannis Sgouromitis/ TWITTER Police have closed to Tower Gateway Bridge 
The woman parked her vehicle on the Tower Bridge Gateway, near Raley, in California. 
Wires are connected to the cars gas tank, according to reports from the scene.
